Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从奶奶去住院开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早上变得忙了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 院子里的花也要浇水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ok~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这么忙的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晨钓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个 早起也变得没那么痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服啊 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过其实更痛苦的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说你洗涤剂放太多了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道他没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这家伙是个外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再帮倒忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ok~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小保～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…保？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩什么时候这么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小保你怎么知道江之岛盖饭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然是因为 这个可是我想出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用 沙丁鱼盖饭 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,thank you 麻理酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树说教钓鱼的朋友 说的就是小春和…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那孩子总一付臭脸 但并不是个坏孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 夏树 你朋友来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是还在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树睡懒觉 这不是好习惯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻嘿咻嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 小樱也认识小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小春超有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 夏树的家人关系超好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小保和麻理酱感情也超好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你们感情好哦 麻理酱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是这种关系？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我还要洗东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 别多嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 你们俩 想钓什么鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想钓个很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在江之岛的 超大的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓到这种东西你就会回去了吗 外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 祝你能钓到大鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小保也一起来钓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我 小雪 夏树一起去钓鱼好不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 又在那里多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不介意啦 不过夏树应该不会答应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近跟他有点闹矛盾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春还真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不好笑吧 我很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上开始就吵吵闹闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管对着什么人都乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不正是小春的优点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春有一种不可思议的力量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融化人心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 跟他在一起可没那么好过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果小春不在的话会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天还能过得这么开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小岛 盖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次抛进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走狗屎运而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是狗屎运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛进去了 进去了 进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多可以进入正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正题…是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是抛进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 我们不是约好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 终于可以往海里抛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 看起来超高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啰嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪开心的话我也开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还不能体会钓鱼的妙趣所在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妙趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是钓鱼的真正的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼不仅仅是钓上来就好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要运用思考 用自己的双手钓上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 我只说一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先找寻目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找吧 海鲈在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我找海鲈在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这么广阔的海面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许在那阴影里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太阳晒得好热嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 那歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到好线索了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鲈喜欢聚集在障碍物周围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保护自己 也容易吃到食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要往那里扔什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是拟饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个带有舌板 类似小鱼的东西叫做米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}米诺_MINNOW指多种小型鱼类，又泛指许多大型鱼类的幼鱼\N特点：纤细，小鳞，MINNOW拟饵模仿得正是这些类似的小鱼。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先用这个钓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让这东西演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在海里游动而吸引鱼类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说就是收饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}retrieve 拟饵钓法中的收饵 收线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,retrieve
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}IT用语辞典 检索出情报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IT用语？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是用线轴卷线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就这么说不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始的话只要卷过来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接卷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向一个方向收线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果目标选得好的话 会有鱼来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘来飘去的那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小岛 盖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你卷太快了 别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 别慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要想象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在水里的拟饵现在到底在哪里游动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼看到的话会有什么感觉那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鲈吃了拟饵的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩的话就配合上动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是感觉上钩的话就扬起钓竿 将钩子钩进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不知道鱼会何时上钩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神 不要放过上钩的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴认真做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小岛 盖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快抬钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 上钩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 用力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别勉强 一直扯的话就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能卷线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强的话鱼会发现是拟饵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要随机应变 现在要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方不会让你如愿的 要好好观察
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像力道一下子变轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 卷线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了×N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急 它要洗鳃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那条鱼挣扎地超厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 别卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别卷了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到最后急了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你太吵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 STELLA SW
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}SHIMANO公司生产的一种纺车轮式路亚轮。\N有smooth、silent、strong的3S之称，价格85000到120000日元不等。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份宁静又强韧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是诱惑人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 如果这附近有大鱼的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是钓鱼船的船长 阿步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才不是说了大鱼之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿步很擅长钓大鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 60厘米以下的根本不能称作为鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上我的船的话 什么都能钓上来给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鲈 鲣鱼 金枪鱼 甚至是剑鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次请务必钓上来给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 不过我要说句话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼不是靠的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是靠技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿步好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明早见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一定要钓上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 明天也带上小保吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 这个我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春好有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就跟我熟拈起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 把这个放到冰箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人份的芝士鳕鱼沙丁鱼球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还会和朋友一起去钓鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要那玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接了个奇怪的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想把这个店怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你讨厌沙丁鱼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一声不说自己就先来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树和小保关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么来这做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起钓鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树不许回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你啊 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会顺利的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说不让用这个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我没对小雪用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这回事好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小保不是很高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪不是也说大家关系好的话比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪你生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我差不多点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老是做这种多余的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你说了大家要关系好点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有那么简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不明白的人类的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白但是我想明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还违反约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最恶劣的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回宇宙或什么地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违反约定确实是小春的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪好生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他现在肯定非常担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想小雪肯定在惦记着小春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟你见面好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小雪说了不要跟过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我说道歉了也还非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起不仅仅是一句话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起就是句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是仅此的话也有无法传递感情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂 谁让我是外星人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如小春不在了你会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才无所谓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那种家伙不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,May any price for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,付出牺牲的表现手法…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有觉得想钓鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不在真安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个自我中心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在不是能说出这种话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚见到你的时候 你在想什么我完全弄不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是托小春的福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大刺刺地闯进别人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总是会觉得想笑不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想快点钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扬起竿来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他停止游之前等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稳住线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和鱼有着『非此不可』的这种绝妙的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要钓上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是你的鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次肯定不会再让它逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓到了 钓上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉好粉好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 还是条大鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照相…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树你帮我拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给小春看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓到海鲈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 关键的时候居然不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春他不会真的回宇宙去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 不管他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点口渴你就！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不是废话啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我不会游泳啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在为我着想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟我见面谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴啊 现在不是说这种事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要淹死了 救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你还在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话 尽做些任性的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不会再说对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没在反省的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我有反省
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有这个的话 小雪你就不会生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小雪要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我总是生气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是外星人 不明白也是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我们就不会吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓到了条很大的海鲈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 撒谎可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的钓到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪撒谎了~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没有骗人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔皮欧卡 那家伙该不会是来交朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要给我蹬鼻子上脸了 外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春一直待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是比任何人都聒噪的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五集 待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
